.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There 5 different types of food: corn, radish, pineapple, kale, plum
House: futuristic, palace, colonial, gothic-revival, farmhouse
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, house, folk, punk, r&b
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, daisy, marigold, azalea
5 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, bridge, monopoly, canasta
1. the futuristic house is the person eating pineapple
2. the swedish house is the person playing bridge
3. the palace house is the fan of punk
4. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating kale
5. the person eating radish is the fan of house
6. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing mah-jongg
7. the person eating plum is the person who growsrose
8. the fan of folk is in the middle
9. the gothic-revival house is on the far left
10. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person playing poker
11. the person playing canastas is on the left or right of the person who growsrose
12. the person who growslily is the fan of pop
13. the colonial house is the person who growsmarigold
14. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person eating corn
15. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the fan of r&b

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Food		|    plum	|     corn	|      pineapple	|     radish	|     kale	|
| House	|   gothic-revival	|    palace	|    futuristic	|    colonial	|    swedish	|
| Game		|     poker	|    canasta	|     mah-jongg	|     monopoly	|      bridge	|
| Music-Genre	|    r&b	|     punk	|     folk	|    house	|      pop	|
| Flower		|   rose	|    azalea	|  daisy	|    marigold	|   lily	|
